items.badge_description: Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 90 distinct venues!

That's 20 different beers from a brewery from one of the folllowing South East Asian countries: Myanmar, Thailand, Malaysia, Philippines, Singapore, Indonesia, East Timor, Vietnam, Cambodia, Laos, Taiwan and Brunei.
